OIvQ.png","title":"Cinnamon chocolate self-saucing pudding","publishedAt":"2018-07-30T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8.9 g","fat":"22.1 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"83.6 g","calories":"2369.3 kJ \/ 564.2 kcal"},"usefulItems":"bowl, jug, ceramic or glass baking dish (23 cm), oven","basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 5m","6 portions"]}